      "role": "user",
      "content": "he says he's fine though, just really sleepy. he's been drinking a lot of water and trying to nap it off. do you think it could just be dehydration or maybe his blood pressure acting up from the travel stress? he's pretty stubborn about not wanting to go to the hospital if it's nothing.",
