    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but he's literally just lying there sleeping now. like, he's not even in pain, he just seems super out of it and sleepy. if i call an ambulance and it turns out to be nothing, it's gonna be a huge mistake and a lot of money wasted. can we just wait an hour to see if he wakes up feeling more normal? isn't it possible he's just hitting a wall from the jet lag?",
